REACTION    beta-D-mannosylphosphodecaprenol + (1->6)-alpha-D-mannosyloligosaccharide = decaprenol phosphate + (1->6)-alpha-D-mannosyl-(1->6)-alpha-D-mannosyl-oligosaccharide [RN:R06046 R06074]
